Wydev packages building scripts
================================

This folder contains scripts to build packages for the wydevice.
Every package will have its build*.sh script that will build a 
tar.gz that can be directly installed under /wymedia.


Build a wybox-extras package
------------------------------

You can build a wybox-extras package (tar.gz) that includes all packages
specified. Follow this steps:

  1. Edit pkgs.conf file to modify the included packages.
  2. ./build-extras.sh

Once finished, file wybox-extras.tar.gz contains all packages and
is ready to be installed in a wybox.


Environment
------------

STLinux 2.3 cross compiler is needed to build packages. You should
also set the compile environment variables by running in this folder

    $ . env-cross-compile.sh

